<v-container> 
    <v-card flat>
        <v-card-title>
            List of user's request
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            <v-text-field
                v-model="search"
                append-icon="mdi-magnify"
                label="Search"
                single-line
                hide-details
            ></v-text-field>                                    
        </v-card-title>

        <v-data-table
            :loading="loadingListOrganizations" loading-text="Loading... Please wait"
            :headers="headers"
            :items="organizations"
            :search="search">                                            
                <template v-slot:item.action="{ item }">
                    <v-icon v-if="!item.status" @click="followOrganization(item)"> mdi-plus-circle-outline </v-icon>
                    <v-icon v-else class="ml-12" @click="unfollowOrganization(item)"> mdi-minus-circle-outline </v-icon>
                </template>
        </v-data-table>
    </v-card>
</v-container>
